This paper is about text summarization and keyword generation using neural networks, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). The paper specifically focuses on research articles, which suggests that it may also be relevant to information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML) applications. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
